message.content: cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV. The paper deals with improving search results in ecommerce catalogs by ranking sentences from product description bullets. This involves natural language processing techniques such as named entity recognition and extractive summarization, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV).
